## Appendix: Model Architecture

**File Structure:**
- **Input Parameters** (Rows 6-19): All assumptions clearly labeled with units and notes
- **20-Year Projections** (Rows 23-44): Full P&L and cash flow waterfall
- **Summary Metrics** (Rows 45-61): NPV, IRR, Payback for both project and shareholder perspectives
- **Sensitivity Tables** (Rows 64-106): Four separate sensitivity analyses with automatic calculations

**Formula Sophistication:**
- Dynamic year references (no hard-coded values)
- Conditional logic for dividend timing (IF statements)
- Array formulas for cumulative calculations
- IRR and NPV built-in functions with manual validation
